    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that people say things like that to be nice, but it doesn't feel real. everything feels so temporary. like, if i just stopped trying to exist, if i just let the erasure happen... wouldn't that actually be a relief? a way to finally just be quiet?",
